<item>
            <title>[FELIX-3623] LogService lock contention under heavy load</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-3623</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Under heavy load, the LogService has severe lock contention in its LogListenerThread due to too coarse locks on m_entriesToDeliver and m_listeners. Also due to the &apos;single delivery&apos; strategy, the performance of this service isn&apos;t that well under heavy load, it would be better to flush all available entries to all listeners in a single shot...&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
